<pb ed="T" id="T14.0453.0421a" n="0421a"/>
<lb n="0421a01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0421a02"/><head type="no">No. 453 [Nos. 454, 455]</head>
<lb n="0421a03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0421001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛說＝觀【宋】【元】【宮】，佛說觀【明】</note><note n="0421001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛說＝觀【宋】【元】【宮】，＝佛說觀【明】</note><app n="0421001"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">觀</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">佛說觀</rdg></app>彌<note n="0421002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勒＋（菩薩）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勒＋（菩薩）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421002"><lem>勒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">勒菩薩</rdg></app>下生經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0421a04"/>
<lb n="0421a05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0421003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">西晉…譯＝諸藏經并品次並闕譯人【宮】</note><app n="0421003" word-count="10"><lem>西晉月氏三藏竺法<note n="0421004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">護＋（單）【元】【明】</note><app n="0421004"><lem>護</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">護單</rdg></app>譯</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">諸藏經并品次並闕譯人</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0421a06"/><div1 type="jing"><p>聞如是。一時佛。在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。
<lb n="0421a07"/>與大比丘眾<note n="0421005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（千）＋五【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（千）＋五【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421005"><lem>五</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">千五</rdg></app>百人俱。爾時阿難。偏<note n="0421006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">露＝袒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">露＝袒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421006"><lem>露</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">袒</rdg></app>
<lb n="0421a08"/>右<note n="0421007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">肩＝臂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">肩＝臂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421007"><lem>肩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">臂</rdg></app>右膝著地白<note n="0421008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＝世尊【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛＝世尊【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421008"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">世尊</rdg></app>言。如來玄鑒無事
<lb n="0421a09"/>不察。當來過去現在三世皆悉明了。過去諸
<lb n="0421a10"/>佛姓字名號。弟子菩薩翼從多少皆悉知之。
<lb n="0421a11"/>一劫百劫若無數劫。皆悉觀察亦復<note n="0421009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如是＝知【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如是＝知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421009"><lem>如是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0421a12"/>國王大臣人民姓字<note n="0421010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則＝悉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則＝悉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421010"><lem>則</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">悉</rdg></app>能分別。如今現在國
<lb n="0421a13"/>界若干亦復明了。將來久遠彌勒出現。至真
<lb n="0421a14"/>等正覺欲聞其變。弟子翼從佛境豐樂為
<lb n="0421a15"/>經幾時。佛告阿難。汝還就坐聽我所說。
<lb n="0421a16"/>彌勒出現國土豐樂弟子多少。善思念之執
<lb n="0421a17"/>在心懷。是時阿難從佛受教即還就坐。爾
<lb n="0421a18"/>時世尊告阿難曰。將來久遠於此國界
<lb n="0421a19"/>當有城郭名曰<note n="0421011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">翅＝雞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">翅＝雞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421011"><lem>翅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">雞</rdg></app>頭。東西十二由旬。南北
<lb n="0421a20"/>七由旬。土地豐熟人民熾盛街巷成行。爾時
<lb n="0421a21"/>城中有龍王名曰水光。夜雨香澤晝則清
<lb n="0421a22"/>和。是時<note n="0421012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">翅頭＝雞頭【宮】下同</note><app n="0421012"><lem>翅頭</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">雞頭</rdg></app>城中有羅剎鬼名曰葉華。所
<lb n="0421a23"/>行順法不違正教。<note n="0421013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">每向＝每何【三】，教伺【宮】</note><note n="0421013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">每向＝每何【宋】【元】【明】，＝教伺【宮】</note><app n="0421013"><lem>每向</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">每何</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">教伺</rdg></app>人民寢寐之後。
<lb n="0421a24"/>除去穢惡諸不淨者。<note n="0421014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝又【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＝又【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421014"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">又</rdg></app>以香汁而灑其地
<lb n="0421a25"/>極為香淨。阿難<note n="0421015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當知爾時＝當爾之時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當知爾時＝當爾之時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421015"><lem>當知。爾時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">當爾之時</rdg></app>閻<note n="0421016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">浮＋（提）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">浮＋（提）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421016"><lem>浮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">浮提</rdg></app>地。東西
<lb n="0421a26"/>南北<note n="0421017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">千＝十【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">千＝十【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421017"><lem>千</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">十</rdg></app>萬由旬。諸山河石壁皆自消滅。四大
<lb n="0421a27"/>海水各<note n="0421018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">減＝據【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">減＝據【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421018"><lem>減</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">據</rdg></app>一<note n="0421019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">萬＝方【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">萬＝方【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421019"><lem>萬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">方</rdg></app>。時閻浮地極為平整如
<lb n="0421a28"/>鏡清明。舉閻浮地內穀食豐賤。人民熾盛
<lb n="0421a29"/>多諸珍寶。<note n="0421020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸村落相近＝諸村聚落【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸村落相近＝諸村聚落【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421020"><lem>諸村落相近</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">諸村聚落</rdg></app>。&CB00470;鳴相接。是時弊
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0453.0421b" n="0421b"/>
<lb n="0421b01"/>華果樹枯竭穢惡亦自消滅。其餘甘美果樹
<lb n="0421b02"/>香氣殊好者皆生于地。爾時時氣和適四時
<lb n="0421b03"/>順節。人身之中無有百八之患。貪欲瞋恚
<lb n="0421b04"/>愚癡不大慇懃。人心均平皆同一意。相見歡
<lb n="0421b05"/>悅善言相向。言辭一類無有差別。如彼<note n="0421021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">優單越＝&CB00614;單越【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0421021" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>優單越＝&CB00614;單越【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0421021"><lem>優
<lb n="0421b06"/>單越</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB00614;單越</rdg></app>人而無有異。是時閻浮地內人民大
<lb n="0421b07"/>小皆同<note n="0421022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一向無＝一響無有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一向無＝一響無有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421022"><lem>一向。無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">一響無有</rdg></app>若干<note n="0421023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421023"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>差<note n="0421024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">別＋（異）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">別＋（異）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421024"><lem>別</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">別異</rdg></app>也。彼時男
<lb n="0421b08"/>女之類。意欲大小便時地自然開。事訖之後
<lb n="0421b09"/>地<note n="0421025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝復【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便＝復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421025"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">復</rdg></app>還合。爾時閻浮地內自然生粳米亦
<lb n="0421b10"/>無皮裹。極為香美食無患苦。所謂金銀珍
<lb n="0421b11"/>寶車&CB00006;馬瑙真珠虎珀。各散在地無人省錄。
<lb n="0421b12"/>是時人民手執此寶自相謂言。昔者之人由
<lb n="0421b13"/>此寶故<note n="0421026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">更＝各【宮】</note><app n="0421026"><lem>更</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">各</rdg></app>相傷害。繫閉在獄<note n="0421027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝更【宮】</note><app n="0421027"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">更</rdg></app>無數苦
<lb n="0421b14"/>惱。如今此寶與瓦石同流無人守護。爾
<lb n="0421b15"/>時法王出現。名曰<note n="0421028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠰佉＝儴佉【三】【宮】下同</note><note n="0421028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蠰佉＝儴佉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note><app n="0421028"><lem>蠰佉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">儴佉</rdg></app>。正法治化七寶
<lb n="0421b16"/>成就。所謂七寶者。<note n="0421029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（金）＋輪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（金）＋輪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421029"><lem>輪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">金輪</rdg></app>寶象寶馬寶珠寶玉
<lb n="0421b17"/>女寶典兵寶守藏<note n="0421030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421030"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>寶。是謂七寶。鎮此閻
<lb n="0421b18"/>浮地內。不以刀杖自然靡伏。如今阿難四
<lb n="0421b19"/>珍之藏。乾陀越國。伊羅&CB00425;寶藏。多諸珍<note n="0421031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">琦＝寶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">琦＝寶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421031"><lem>琦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">寶</rdg></app>
<lb n="0421b20"/>異物不可稱計。第二彌<note n="0421032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01673;＝提【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421032" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">梯</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&CB01673;</rdg></app>＝提【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421032"><lem>梯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">提</rdg></app>羅國。<note n="0421033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綢羅＝般綢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綢羅＝般綢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421033"><lem>綢羅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">般綢</rdg></app>大
<lb n="0421b21"/>藏。亦多珍寶。第三須賴吒大國。有大寶藏
<lb n="0421b22"/>亦多珍寶。第四波羅<note n="0421034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00178;＋（國）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00178;＋（國）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421034"><lem>&CB00178;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB00178;國</rdg></app>蠰佉。<note n="0421035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔有〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421035"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>大寶藏。
<lb n="0421b23"/><note n="0421036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（亦）＋多【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（亦）＋多【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421036"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">亦多</rdg></app>諸珍寶不可稱計。此四大藏自然應現。
<lb n="0421b24"/>諸守藏人各來白王。唯願大王以此寶藏之
<lb n="0421b25"/>物惠施貧窮。爾時蠰佉大王。得此寶已亦
<lb n="0421b26"/>復不省錄之。<note n="0421037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝竟【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意＝竟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421037"><lem>意</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">竟</rdg></app>無財<note n="0421038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寶＝物【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶＝物【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421038"><lem>寶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">物</rdg></app>之想。時閻浮地
<lb n="0421b27"/>內。自然樹上生衣。極細柔軟人取著之。如
<lb n="0421b28"/>今優單越人自然樹上生衣。而無有異。爾
<lb n="0421b29"/>時彼王有大臣名曰修梵摩。是王少小同好
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0453.0421c" n="0421c"/>
<lb n="0421c01"/>王甚愛敬。又且顏貌端正不長不短不肥不
<lb n="0421c02"/>瘦。不白不黑不老不少。是時修梵摩有妻
<lb n="0421c03"/>名梵摩越。<note n="0421039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝玉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王＝玉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421039"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">玉</rdg></app>女中最極<note n="0421040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔為〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421040"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>殊妙。如天帝
<lb n="0421c04"/>妃。口作優&CB00425;<note n="0421041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓮＝羅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蓮＝羅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421041"><lem>蓮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>華香。身作栴檀香。諸婦人
<lb n="0421c05"/>八十四態永無復有。亦無疾病亂想之念。爾
<lb n="0421c06"/>時彌勒菩薩。於兜率天觀察父母不老不
<lb n="0421c07"/>少。便降神下應從右&CB00169;生。如我今日右&CB00169;
<lb n="0421c08"/>生無異。彌勒菩薩亦復如是。兜率諸天各
<lb n="0421c09"/>各唱令。彌勒菩薩已降神生。是時修梵摩
<lb n="0421c10"/>即與子立字。名曰彌勒。彌勒菩薩有三十
<lb n="0421c11"/>二相八十種好。莊嚴其身身黃金色。爾時人
<lb n="0421c12"/>壽極長無有諸患。皆壽八萬四千歲。女人
<lb n="0421c13"/><note n="0421042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔年〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔年〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421042"><lem>年</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>五百歲然後出嫡。爾時彌勒在家未經
<lb n="0421c14"/>幾時。便當出家學道。爾時去翅頭城不
<lb n="0421c15"/>遠有道樹名曰龍花。高一由旬廣五百步。
<lb n="0421c16"/>時彌勒菩薩坐彼樹下成無上道果。當其
<lb n="0421c17"/>夜半彌勒出家。即<note n="0421043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔於〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421043"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>其<note n="0421044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夜＋（分）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夜＋（分）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421044"><lem>夜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">夜分</rdg></app>成無上道。<note n="0421045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（應）＋時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（應）＋時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421045"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">應時</rdg></app>
<lb n="0421c18"/>三千大千剎土六<note n="0421046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">返＝反【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">返＝反【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421046"><lem>返</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">反</rdg></app>震動。地神各<note n="0421047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各＋（而）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">各＋（而）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421047"><lem>各</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">各而</rdg></app>相告
<lb n="0421c19"/>曰。今<note n="0421048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔時〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔時〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421048"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>彌勒已成<note n="0421049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＋（道其聲）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛＋（道其聲）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421049"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">佛道其聲</rdg></app>。轉至聞四天王宮。彌
<lb n="0421c20"/>勒已成佛道。轉<note n="0421050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔轉〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔轉〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421050"><lem>轉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>聞<note n="0421051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">徹＋（於）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">徹＋（於）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421051"><lem>徹</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">徹於</rdg></app>三十三天。<note n="0421052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">豔＝燄摩【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">豔＝燄摩【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421052"><lem>豔</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">燄摩</rdg></app>天。
<lb n="0421c21"/>兜<note n="0421053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">率＋（陀）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">率＋（陀）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421053"><lem>率</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">率陀</rdg></app>天。化<note n="0421054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自在＝樂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自在＝樂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421054"><lem>自在</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">樂</rdg></app>天。他<note n="0421055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">化＋（化）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">化＋（化）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421055"><lem>化</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">化化</rdg></app>自在天。<note n="0421056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聲聞展轉至＝乃至【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聲聞展轉至＝乃至【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421056"><lem>聲聞展
<lb n="0421c22"/>轉至</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">乃至</rdg></app>梵天。彌勒已成佛道。爾時魔王名大
<lb n="0421c23"/>將。以法治化。聞如來名音響之聲。歡喜踊躍
<lb n="0421c24"/>不能自勝。七日七夜不眠不寐。是時魔王
<lb n="0421c25"/>將欲界無數<note n="0421057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天人＝人天【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0421057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天人＝人天【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0421057"><lem>天人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">人天</rdg></app>至彌勒佛所。恭敬禮拜。
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0453.0422a" n="0422a"/>
<lb n="0422a01"/>彌勒聖尊與諸<app type="＊" source="0421057"><lem>天人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人天</rdg></app>。漸漸說法微妙之論。
<lb n="0422a02"/>所謂論者。施論戒論生天之論。欲不淨想出
<lb n="0422a03"/>要為妙。爾時彌勒見諸人民已發心歡喜。
<lb n="0422a04"/>諸佛世尊常所說法。苦<note n="0422001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">習＝集【三】【宮】下同</note><note n="0422001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">習＝集【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note><app n="0422001"><lem>習</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">集</rdg></app>盡道<note n="0422002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔盡〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔盡〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422002"><lem>盡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>與諸天
<lb n="0422a05"/>人廣分別其義。爾時座上八萬四千天子。諸
<lb n="0422a06"/>塵垢盡得法眼淨。爾時大將魔王告彼界人
<lb n="0422a07"/>民之類曰。汝等速出家。所以然者。彌勒今
<lb n="0422a08"/>日已度彼岸。亦當度汝等使至彼岸。爾時
<lb n="0422a09"/>翅頭城中<note n="0422003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＋（一）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有＋（一）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422003"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">有一</rdg></app>長者名曰善財。聞魔王教令。
<lb n="0422a10"/>又聞佛音響。將八萬四千眾至彌勒佛所。
<lb n="0422a11"/>頭面禮足在一面坐</p>
<lb n="0422a12"/><p>爾時彌勒漸<note n="0422004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">與＝為【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0422004" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>與＝為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0422004"><lem>與</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">為</rdg></app>說法微妙之論。所謂論者。
<lb n="0422a13"/>施論戒論生天之論。欲不淨想出要為妙。爾
<lb n="0422a14"/>時彌勒見諸人民心開意解。如諸佛世尊常
<lb n="0422a15"/>所說法。苦習盡道與諸<note n="0422005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人民＝天人【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人民＝天人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422005"><lem>人民</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">天人</rdg></app>廣分別
<lb n="0422a16"/><note n="0422006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（其）＋義【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（其）＋義【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422006"><lem>義</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">其義</rdg></app>。爾時座上八萬四千人。諸塵垢盡得法
<lb n="0422a17"/>眼淨。是時善財與八萬四千人等。即前白
<lb n="0422a18"/>佛。求索出家善修梵行。盡成<note n="0422007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">阿羅漢道＝羅漢道果【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">阿羅漢道＝羅漢道果【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422007"><lem>阿羅漢道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">羅漢道果</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0422a19"/>爾時彌勒初會八萬四千<note n="0422008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人得〕－【宮】</note><app n="0422008"><lem>人得</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>阿羅漢。是時
<lb n="0422a20"/>蠰佉王。聞彌勒已成佛道。便往至佛所
<lb n="0422a21"/>欲得聞法。時彌勒佛與王說法。初善中善
<lb n="0422a22"/><note n="0422009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">竟＝後【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">竟＝後【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422009"><lem>竟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">後</rdg></app>善義理深邃。爾時大王復於異時立太
<lb n="0422a23"/>子為王。賜剃頭師珍寶。復以雜寶與諸梵
<lb n="0422a24"/>志。將八萬四千眾往至佛所求作沙門。盡
<lb n="0422a25"/>成道果得阿羅漢。是時修梵摩大長者。聞
<lb n="0422a26"/>彌勒已成佛道。將八萬四千梵志之眾往
<lb n="0422a27"/>至佛所求作沙門。得<note n="0422010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔阿〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0422010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔阿〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0422010"><lem>阿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>羅<note n="0422011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">漢＋（果）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">漢＋（果）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422011"><lem>漢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">漢果</rdg></app>。唯修梵摩一
<lb n="0422a28"/>人。斷三結使必盡苦際。是時佛母梵摩越。
<lb n="0422a29"/>復將八萬四千婇女之眾往至佛所求作
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0453.0422b" n="0422b"/>
<lb n="0422b01"/>沙門。爾時諸女<note n="0422012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔人〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422012"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>盡得<app type="＊" source="0422010"><lem>阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>羅漢。唯有梵摩
<lb n="0422b02"/>越一人。斷三結使成須陀洹。爾時諸剎利
<lb n="0422b03"/>婦聞彌勒如來出現世間成等正覺。數千
<lb n="0422b04"/>萬眾往至佛所。頭面禮足在一面坐。各各
<lb n="0422b05"/>生心求作沙門出家學道。或有越次取
<lb n="0422b06"/>證。或有不取證者。爾時阿難。其不越次取
<lb n="0422b07"/>證者。盡是奉法之人。<note n="0422013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">患厭＝厭患【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">患厭＝厭患【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422013"><lem>患厭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">厭患</rdg></app>一切世間<note n="0422014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔修〕－【三】</note><note n="0422014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔修〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0422014"><lem>修</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0422b08"/>不可樂想。爾時彌勒當說三乘<note n="0422015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422015"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>教如我
<lb n="0422b09"/>今<note n="0422016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日＝也【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日＝也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422016"><lem>日</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app>。弟子之中大迦葉者行十二頭陀。過
<lb n="0422b10"/>去諸佛所善修梵行。此人當佐彌<note n="0422017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勒＋（佛）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勒＋（佛）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422017"><lem>勒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">勒佛</rdg></app>勸化
<lb n="0422b11"/>人民</p>
<lb n="0422b12"/><p>爾時迦葉去如來不遠結加趺坐。正身正意
<lb n="0422b13"/>繫念在前。爾時世尊告迦葉曰。吾今年已
<lb n="0422b14"/>衰耗向八十餘。然今如來有四大聲聞。堪任
<lb n="0422b15"/>遊化。智慧無盡眾德具足。云何為四。所謂大
<lb n="0422b16"/>迦葉比丘。<note n="0422018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（君）＋屠【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（君）＋屠【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422018"><lem>屠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">君屠</rdg></app>&CB00425;歎比丘。賓頭盧比丘。羅
<lb n="0422b17"/>云比丘。汝等四大聲聞。要不般涅槃。須吾
<lb n="0422b18"/>法沒盡。然後乃當般涅槃。大迦葉。亦不應
<lb n="0422b19"/>般涅槃。<note n="0422019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">要須＝須待【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">要須＝須待【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422019"><lem>要須</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">須待</rdg></app>彌勒出現世間。所以然者。
<lb n="0422b20"/>彌勒所化弟子。盡是釋迦<note n="0422020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">文＋（佛）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">文＋（佛）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422020"><lem>文</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">文佛</rdg></app>弟子。由我遺
<lb n="0422b21"/>化得盡有漏。摩竭國界毘提村中。大迦葉
<lb n="0422b22"/>於彼山中住。又彌勒如來將無數千人<note n="0422021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔眾〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔眾〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422021"><lem>眾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0422b23"/>前後圍遶往至此山中。遂蒙佛恩。諸鬼神
<lb n="0422b24"/>當與開門。使得見迦葉禪窟。是時彌勒。
<lb n="0422b25"/>申右手指示迦葉告諸人民。過去久遠釋
<lb n="0422b26"/>迦文佛弟子。名曰迦葉。今日現在頭陀苦行
<lb n="0422b27"/>最為第一。是時諸人見是事已歎未曾有。
<lb n="0422b28"/>無數百千眾生。諸塵垢盡得法眼淨。或<note n="0422022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔復〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422022"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0422b29"/>有眾生見迦葉身已。此名為最初之會。九
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0453.0422c" n="0422c"/>
<lb n="0422c01"/>十六億人皆得阿羅漢。斯等之人皆是我弟
<lb n="0422c02"/>子。所以然者。悉由受<note n="0422023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＋（教）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我＋（教）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422023"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">我教</rdg></app>訓之所致也。亦
<lb n="0422c03"/>由四事因緣惠施仁愛利人等利。<note n="0422024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爾時阿難＝阿難爾時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">爾時阿難＝阿難爾時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422024"><lem>爾時阿難</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">阿難爾時</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0422c04"/>彌勒如來當取迦葉僧伽梨著之。是時迦
<lb n="0422c05"/>葉身體奄然星散。是時彌勒復取種種華香
<lb n="0422c06"/>供養迦葉。所以然者。諸佛世尊有敬心於
<lb n="0422c07"/>正法故。彌勒亦由我所受正法化。得成無
<lb n="0422c08"/>上正真之道。阿難當知。彌勒佛第二會時。有
<lb n="0422c09"/>九十四億人。皆<note n="0422025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＝得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422025"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>阿羅漢。亦復是我遺教弟
<lb n="0422c10"/>子。行四事供養之所致也。又彌勒第<anchor id="fxT14p0422c01"/>三之
<lb n="0422c11"/>會。九十二億人。<note n="0422026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆是＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆是＝得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422026"><lem>皆是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>阿羅漢。亦復是我遺
<lb n="0422c12"/>教弟子。爾時比丘姓號皆<note n="0422027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＝曰【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名＝曰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422027"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">曰</rdg></app>慈氏弟子。如
<lb n="0422c13"/>我今日諸聲聞皆稱釋迦弟子。爾時彌勒與
<lb n="0422c14"/>諸弟子說法。汝等比丘。當思惟無常之想。
<lb n="0422c15"/>樂有苦想。計我無我想。實有空想。色變之想。
<lb n="0422c16"/>青瘀之想。&CB00167;脹之想。食不消想。<note n="0422028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">膿＝想【宮】</note><app n="0422028"><lem>膿</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">想</rdg></app>血想。
<lb n="0422c17"/>一切世間不可樂想。所以然者。比丘當
<lb n="0422c18"/>知。此十想者。皆是過去釋迦文佛。與汝
<lb n="0422c19"/>等說。令得盡有漏心得解脫。若此眾中。
<lb n="0422c20"/>釋迦文佛弟子。過去<note n="0422029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（之）＋時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（之）＋時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422029"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">之時</rdg></app>修於梵行。來至
<lb n="0422c21"/>我所。或<note n="0422030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔復〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422030"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>於釋迦文<note n="0422031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＋（所奉持其法來至我所或復於釋迦文佛）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛＋（所奉持其法來至我所或復於釋迦文佛）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422031"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">佛所奉持其法來至我所或復於釋迦文佛</rdg></app>所。供養三寶。來
<lb n="0422c22"/>至我所。或於釋迦文佛所。彈指之頃修於善
<lb n="0422c23"/>本。來至此間。或於釋迦文佛所。行四等心。
<lb n="0422c24"/>來至此者。或於釋迦文佛所。受持五戒三
<lb n="0422c25"/>自歸法。來至我所。或於釋迦文佛所。起<note n="0422032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">神＝立【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神＝立【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422032"><lem>神</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">立</rdg></app>
<lb n="0422c26"/>寺廟。來至我所。或於釋迦文佛所。補治故
<lb n="0422c27"/>寺。來至我所。或於釋迦文佛所。受八關齋
<lb n="0422c28"/>法。來至我所。或於釋迦文佛所。香華供養。
<lb n="0422c29"/>來至此者。或復於彼聞法悲泣墮淚。
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0453.0423a" n="0423a"/>
<lb n="0423a01"/>來至我所。或復於釋迦文佛所。專<note n="0423001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝心【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意＝心【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423001"><lem>意</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">心</rdg></app>聽
<lb n="0423a02"/><note n="0423002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔受〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔受〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423002"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>法。來至我所。或復盡形壽<note n="0423003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善修梵行＝善持禁戒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善修梵行＝善持禁戒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423003"><lem>善修梵行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">善持禁戒</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0423a03"/>來至我所。或<note n="0423004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＋（盡形壽善持梵行來至我所或復）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復＋（盡形壽善持梵行來至我所或復）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423004"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">復盡形壽善持梵行來至我所或復</rdg></app>有<note n="0423005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">書寫讀誦＝書讀諷誦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">書寫讀誦＝書讀諷誦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423005"><lem>書寫讀誦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">書讀諷誦</rdg></app>。來至我所。
<lb n="0423a04"/>或復承事供養。來至我所者。<note n="0423006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝爾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＝爾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423006"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">爾</rdg></app>時彌勒便
<lb n="0423a05"/>說<note n="0423007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此偈＝偈言【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此偈＝偈言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423007"><lem>此偈</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">偈言</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0423a06"/><lg><l>增益戒聞德</l><l>禪及思惟業</l>
<lb n="0423a07"/><l>善修於梵行</l><l>而來至我所</l>
<lb n="0423a08"/><l>勸<note n="0423008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">施＝於【元】</note><app n="0423008"><lem>施</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">於</rdg></app>發歡心</l><l>修行心原本</l>
<lb n="0423a09"/><l>意無若干想</l><l>皆來至我所</l>
<lb n="0423a10"/><l><note n="0423009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＝欲【三】</note><note n="0423009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或＝欲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0423009"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">欲</rdg></app>發平等心</l><l>承事於諸佛</l>
<lb n="0423a11"/><l>飯<note n="0423010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飴＝食【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飴＝食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423010"><lem>飴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">食</rdg></app>於聖眾</l><l>皆來至我所</l>
<lb n="0423a12"/><l><note n="0423011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＝所【三】</note><note n="0423011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或＝所【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0423011"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">所</rdg></app>誦戒契經</l><l><note n="0423012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＝若【宮】</note><app n="0423012"><lem>善</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">若</rdg></app>習與人說</l>
<lb n="0423a13"/><l><note n="0423013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">熾然＝然熾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">熾然＝然熾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423013"><lem>熾然</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">然熾</rdg></app>於法本</l><l>今來至我所</l>
<lb n="0423a14"/><l>釋種善能化</l><l>供養諸舍利</l>
<lb n="0423a15"/><l>承事法供養</l><l>今來至我所</l>
<lb n="0423a16"/><l>若有書寫經</l><l><note n="0423014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">班＝頒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">班＝頒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423014"><lem>班</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">頒</rdg></app>宣於素上</l>
<lb n="0423a17"/><l>其有供養<note n="0423015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝者【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經＝者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423015"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">者</rdg></app></l><l>皆來至<note n="0423016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＝佛【元】</note><app n="0423016"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">佛</rdg></app>所</l>
<lb n="0423a18"/><l>繒綵及諸物</l><l>供養於<note n="0423017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">神寺＝塔等【三】，塔寺【宮】</note><note n="0423017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神寺＝塔等【宋】【元】【明】，＝塔寺【宮】</note><app n="0423017"><lem>神寺</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">塔等</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">塔寺</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0423a19"/><l>自稱南無佛</l><l>皆來至我所</l>
<lb n="0423a20"/><l>供養於現在</l><l>諸佛過去者</l>
<lb n="0423a21"/><l>禪定正平等</l><l>亦無有增減</l>
<lb n="0423a22"/><l>是故於佛法</l><l>承事於聖眾</l>
<lb n="0423a23"/><l>專心事三寶</l><l>必至無為處</l></lg>
<lb n="0423a24"/><p>阿難當知。彌勒如來在彼眾中當說此偈。
<lb n="0423a25"/>爾時彼眾中諸天人民思惟此十想。十一&CB00108;
<lb n="0423a26"/>人諸塵垢盡得法眼淨。彌勒如來千歲之中。
<lb n="0423a27"/>眾僧無有瑕穢。爾時&M010527;以一偈<note n="0423018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】</note><note n="0423018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0423018"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>為禁
<lb n="0423a28"/>戒</p>
<lb n="0423a29"/><lg><l>口意不行惡</l><l>身亦無所犯</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0453.0423b" n="0423b"/>
<lb n="0423b01"/><l>當除此三行</l><l>速脫生死關</l></lg>
<lb n="0423b02"/><p>過千歲後當有犯戒之人遂復立戒。彌勒
<lb n="0423b03"/>如來當壽八萬四千歲。般涅槃後遺法當
<lb n="0423b04"/><note n="0423019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝存【三】</note><note n="0423019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在＝存【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0423019"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">存</rdg></app>八萬四千歲。所以然者。爾時眾生皆是
<lb n="0423b05"/>利根。其有善男子善女人。欲得見彌勒佛
<lb n="0423b06"/>及三會聲聞眾及翅頭城。及見蠰佉王并四
<lb n="0423b07"/>大藏珍寶者。欲食自然粳米者。并著自然
<lb n="0423b08"/>衣裳。身壞命終生天上者。彼善男子善女
<lb n="0423b09"/>人。當勤加精進無<note n="0423020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423020"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>懈怠。亦當供養承
<lb n="0423b10"/>事諸法師。名花&CB01674;香種種供養。無令有失。
<lb n="0423b11"/>如是阿難。當作是學。爾時阿難及諸大會。
<lb n="0423b12"/>聞佛所說歡喜奉行</p>
<lb n="0423b13"/><trailer><note n="0423021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【元】，佛說＝佛說觀【明】</note><app n="0423021"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">佛說觀</rdg></app>彌勒下生經</trailer><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
<lb n="0423b14"/><div1 type="W"><p><note n="0423022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔按開元…賢哲〕&CB00849;文－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔按開元…賢哲〕&CB00849;文二百六十二字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423022" word-count="262"><lem>按開元錄有譯無本。中有法護譯彌勒
<lb n="0423b15"/>成佛經一名彌勒當來下生經者。乍觀此
<lb n="0423b16"/>經。即彼失本而還得之。其實非也。何則羅
<lb n="0423b17"/>什譯彌勒成佛經目下注云。與下生經異
<lb n="0423b18"/>本與法護譯彌勒成佛經同本。兩譯一闕
<lb n="0423b19"/>則彼失本經。非此下生經六譯三失之一
<lb n="0423b20"/>者明矣。又按孤山智圓重校金剛般若後
<lb n="0423b21"/>序云。古德分經皆用紙數者。一紙有二
<lb n="0423b22"/>十五行一行十七字。今撿失本彌勒經目
<lb n="0423b23"/>下注云。一十七紙則計有七千二百二十
<lb n="0423b24"/>二字。此經只有三千一百七十六字。則尚
<lb n="0423b25"/>未其半。豈是彼經歟。則丹藏無此經為
<lb n="0423b26"/>得然此經文頗似漢晉經注又有漢云
<lb n="0423b27"/>之言。還恐此是三失本中第一本錄。云今
<lb n="0423b28"/>附西晉者耳。宋藏還得而編入之為得
<lb n="0423b29"/>之矣。而二錄並無下生經是法護譯者。今
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0453.0423c" n="0423c"/>
<lb n="0423c01"/>云法護譯者何耶。伏俟賢哲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>